Czech Premier Says Can’t Exclude Drop in 2012 Budget Revenue

-- B y   A n d r e a   D u d i k
-- 
2011-09-25T10:33:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/czech-premier-says-can-t-exclude-drop-in-2012-budget-revenue.html
Czech Premier Petr Necas said he
can’t exclude the possibility of a drop in revenue in 2012
budget, he said on CT24 television today. Still, he said it was
too early to say whether such a drop will take place.  To contact the reporter on this story:
